& [SOPHypergraphRecord] is local_ai_manager_primary_090
  + [record_type] is periphery_realization
  + [focus_subject] is local AI manager primary
  + [inside] is LM Studio local manager, lightweight SOP context stream, direct endpoint transport, handoff threshold, OpenAI Codex worker on demand, and allowance conservation
  + [boundary] is local manager proposes, local validator checks routine output, OpenAI Codex enters only for high-demand reasoning, repo mutation, authority repair, tests, commits, pushes, or launch review
