  = realization: the target architecture is local-first manager operation, not OpenAI Codex mediating every manager tick through LM Studio
  = caution: Codex-mediated LM Studio remains useful as diagnostic/bootstrap but it defeats the allowance-conservation goal if used for routine manager duty
  = wisdom: the correct economy is cheap local attention for queue awareness and expensive Codex attention only when the task crosses a named handoff threshold
  = implementation_status: correction encoded; direct LM Studio endpoint manager runner is the next ready build surface

